infoLinks.urlText: Pacific Highway Crows Nest, temporary bus stop closure
infoLinks.content:
• From 4am Monday 11 January 2021 to end of June 2024, Sydney Metro work will result in the closure of bus stop Pacific Hwy after Oxley St (206515).
  • The alternative stop will be Pacific Hwy after Albany St (206514) for route 114, 144, 252, 254, 265, 286, 287, 290, 291 and 320 services.
